    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.quest50C5F52359BCCD70.title": "达到磐石级！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.quest5128C6A1AC72BAF9.description1": "保持电脑（PC）整洁是成为一名优秀训练家的必要条件！",
