    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.quest68F841C646C9F9E1.title": "达到黄金级！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.quest6CF329242494B90.title": "复活5个化石",
    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.quest6F67FB69D101E731.description1": "别担心，到了该进化的时候它们会告诉你的！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.quest779E4A54071E24F4.task.5543412274239403997.title": "天王级",
    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.quest779E4A54071E24F4.title": "达到天王级！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.quest78D53D4EAFB02D71.task.75601552986857807.title": "将一只宝可梦升至100级",
    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.quest81919C8B667A323.task.496719626182903981.title": "将一只宝可梦升至50级",
    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.questF9034B6551CB99E.description1": "要让宝可梦&e升级&r，你可以与野生宝可梦对战、捕捉野生宝可梦，或者使用糖果！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.questF9034B6551CB99E.task.945656568559401934.title": "升级10次",
    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.questF9034B6551CB99E.title": "完成10次宝可梦升级",
    "ftbquests.chapter.beginner.title": "训练家等级",
    "ftbquests.chapter.cobble_berries.quest3AB4EA1D879A42B9.task.6400843828832053611.title": "收集所有方可梦树果",
    "ftbquests.chapter.cobble_berries.quest3AB4EA1D879A42B9.title": "方可梦树果收集完成！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.cobble_berries.title": "方可梦树果",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest127DAB9080BE7D68.description1": "&6个体值&r（IV）是参与决定每只宝可梦能力的一组数值。个体值与生俱来，无法改变。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest127DAB9080BE7D68.description2": "&6基础点数&r（EV）是击败宝可梦后，除了经验值外可以获得的另一项数值。累积基础点数可以提升能力值。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest127DAB9080BE7D68.task.323715353840508428.title": "个体值与基础点数（IV与EV）",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest12A48976D7B8F138.description1": "提升宝可梦的等级是方可梦中的重要一环。这能让它们在对战中拥有更高的能力，学会新招式，甚至在满足条件时发生进化。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest12A48976D7B8F138.description2": "对于带有职能的宝可梦来说，等级会影响它们的工作速度与资源产量。查看JEI/EMI配方以了解哪些能力会影响这两者。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest12A48976D7B8F138.title": "提升宝可梦等级",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest179E6CCD0172DEE3.description1": "供奉&6太阳精华&r可以提升&6太阳团体战雕像&r的阶级。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest179E6CCD0172DEE3.description2": "这不会重新随机分配该雕像的宝可梦。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest179E6CCD0172DEE3.subtitle": "升级阶级",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest227824A991F8325C.description1": "寻找特定的宝可梦可能会很枯燥，而高阶的&6太阳团体战雕像&r将从稀有或罕见的生成池中随机抽取宝可梦！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest227824A991F8325C.description2": "&6神秘曲奇&r可用于重新随机分配该雕像的宝可梦。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest227824A991F8325C.subtitle": "重新随机宝可梦",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest2A029AD9B654F48.description1": "散布于世界各地的&6究极道具球&r中可以找到宇宙星尘。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest2A029AD9B654F48.description2": "似乎是来自另一个维度的宝可梦掉落的...",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest2A7540BBB7D13AFD.description1": "Placing PCs everywhere to sort out your Pokémon can be a hassle. The &6Pocket PC&r is a convenient option when you're on the go for managing your strorage.",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest2A7540BBB7D13AFD.description2": "The &6Poké Mart&r will start stocking it once you reach &6Gold Tier&r.",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest2C65A2C19293943D.description1": "&6化石复原&r能从化石中提取宝可梦的基因并让它们重获新生！放置一个&6化石分析仪&r，在它顶部放一个&6数据显示器&r，并在旁边放一个&6复原培养皿&r。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest2C65A2C19293943D.description2": "将化石放入分析仪，并在培养皿内填满树苗或树果等有机物即可开始复原。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest2C65A2C19293943D.description3": "完成复原后拿着任意精灵球右键培养皿，即可让它加入你的同行队伍中。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest2C65A2C19293943D.title": "创造生命",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest2F3C5A12C91B07A9.description1": "&6Mythical Pokémon&r can be found via &6Mystery Gift!&r",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest2F3C5A12C91B07A9.description2": "The main way to obtain these is purchasing them for an insanely high price.",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest2F3C5A12C91B07A9.description3": "Each of the 6 villagers also has a unique villager gift they'll give you at maximum friendship.",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest2F3C5A12C91B07A9.description4": "They can only be gotten once you reach the &6Prismatic Trainer tier&r. ",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest32CD8E2368E6B4BD.description1": "你的朋友说服了你来玩这个整合包，但你其实并不喜欢方块宝可梦？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest32CD8E2368E6B4BD.description2": "&n&a完全没问题！&r",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest32CD8E2368E6B4BD.description3": "虽然名字里带有方可梦，但它们是可选的。你完全把这个整合包可以当成基础的&6Society: Sunlit Valley&r来玩！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest32CD8E2368E6B4BD.description4": "话虽如此，但宝可梦不仅仅是可选的支线。与它们会使你的农场变得更好，例如安排它们为你种田和挖矿！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest32CD8E2368E6B4BD.task.4280089414261917624.title": "明白了！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest32CD8E2368E6B4BD.title": "我只想种田...",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest375BD349F42BAC72.description1": "考古是方可梦的核心玩法之一。记得在背包里准备一把&6刷子&r！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest375BD349F42BAC72.description2": "如果运气好的话，你可能会找到&6化石&r。当有了合适的技术，你就能将它复原成宝可梦。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest375BD349F42BAC72.task.5610415812146672588.title": "任意宝可梦化石",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest375BD349F42BAC72.title": "搜寻宝可梦",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3A51DD86507A83F7.description1": "你可以安排安排不同属性的宝可梦探索&6神秘矿井&r以获取各种资源。这是一趟漫长的旅程，所以需要持续为它们供应&6树果&r！树果越贵，收获越好。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3A51DD86507A83F7.description2": "-&6地面属性&r：考古",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3A51DD86507A83F7.description3": "-&6岩石属性&r：挖掘主世界、下界或骷髅洞穴的矿石（不同维度的矿石需要不同的食物）",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3A51DD86507A83F7.description4": "-&6龙属性&r：发掘宝石和金币",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3A51DD86507A83F7.description5": "-&6幽灵属性&r：寻找怪物掉落物",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3A5238FBDCD86BD6.description1": "当两种不同的&6树果&r相邻种植时，有很小的几率会变异出更有价值的树果。请查看&6JEI/EMI&r以了解可能的变异。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3A5238FBDCD86BD6.task.3944613492798218985.title": "任意变异树果",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3A5238FBDCD86BD6.title": "变异树果",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3BD199B4A938437F.description1": "&6园艺站&r应该是你最早拥有的工作站之一！它能让有特定职能的宝可梦来管理你的农场。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3BD199B4A938437F.description2": "所有工作中的宝可梦都会根据自身的等级，在工作站周围的区域内执行相应的动作。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3BD199B4A938437F.description3": "-&6水属性&r：浇灌工作范围内的作物",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3BD199B4A938437F.description4": "-&6草属性&r：促进工作范围内作物的生长",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3BD199B4A938437F.description5": "-&6恶属性&r：击败野生宝可梦以获取经验道具",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3BD199B4A938437F.description6": "-&6一般属性&r：照料附近&6牧场小窝&r中的宝可梦或挤奶",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3BD199B4A938437F.description7": "-&6妖精属性&r：采集附近&6牧场小窝&r中的宝可梦掉落物",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest3BD199B4A938437F.description8": "- &6Flying&r - Harvests Cobble Berries in an area, with a chance to eat them",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest41E167BF05E599AA.description1": "The &6Pasture Block&r allows your Pokémon to roam free and do \"stuff\" with each other!",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest41E167BF05E599AA.description2": "Pokémon in the pasture might lay eggs! These are a way you can get multiple or better versions of a Pokémon. ",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest41E167BF05E599AA.description3": "The breeding methods match the original games, so information on those is applicable here.",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest41E167BF05E599AA.title": "Breeding Mons",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest42C6D7A0CA188636.description1": "就像普通的农场动物一样，部分宝可梦也可以被饲养并获取各种资源！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest42C6D7A0CA188636.description2": "需要让它们呆在&6牧场小窝&r中，并持续喂食&6树果&r。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest42C6D7A0CA188636.description3": "牧场小窝产物与宝可梦的&6HP&r和&6亲密度&r有关，数值越高，掉落物就越好。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest42C6D7A0CA188636.description4": "如果宝可梦可以产奶，你可以使用&6挤奶桶&r来为它们挤奶。大多数宝可梦如果生命值超过5颗心，也可以用&6魔法剪刀&r对其进行采集。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest42C6D7A0CA188636.subtitle": "哞哞鲜奶？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest43B535325E3201AE.description1": "当你拥有的宝可梦总数超过6只时，&6电脑&r可以让你存取宝可梦。它们散布在世界各地的宝可补给站中。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest43B535325E3201AE.description2": "你也可以在&6友好商店&r中购买电脑，或者达到特定的训练家等级后作为&6免费&r的奖励获得。\n",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest43B535325E3201AE.rich_description1": "磐石级（点击此处）。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest43DCB8601B40FB9A.description1": "达到&b钻石级&r后，阳光联盟将会认定你为阳光谷的核心人物！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest43DCB8601B40FB9A.description2": "你将获得一个&6训练家平台&r作为奖励，来自四面八方的训练家都会聚集于此进行对战。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest43DCB8601B40FB9A.description3": "训练家的实力将与你同行队伍中宝可梦的等级相匹配，因此无论等级高低，你都能锻炼你的宝可梦。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest43DCB8601B40FB9A.description4": "每获得&610场胜利&r，你在对战后获得的奖金就会增加一倍，同时训练家也会变得更加难以对付...",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest43DCB8601B40FB9A.title": "建立你的道馆",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4441EAF3D8A0A3CB.description1": "有关传说宝可梦内容仍在开发中，最终版本可能会有较大改动。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4441EAF3D8A0A3CB.description2": "先去做个星之妖精吧！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4441EAF3D8A0A3CB.title": "挑战传说宝可梦",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest49B1EE5FD231CF30.description1": "&6治疗仪&r可以完全恢复你同行队伍中所有宝可梦的的体力和状态。它们散布在世界各地的宝可补给站中。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest49B1EE5FD231CF30.description2": "你也可以在&6友好商店&r中购买治疗仪，或者达到特定的训练家等级后作为&6免费&r的奖励获得。\n",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest49B1EE5FD231CF30.rich_description1": "嫰枝级（点击此处）",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest49B1EE5FD231CF30.title": "居家恢复",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4AA0BB45D0A6782F.description1": "宝可梦每项&6个体值&r最高为31，最低为0。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4AA0BB45D0A6782F.description2": "通常情况下，你会希望个体值越高越好，以让你的宝可梦达到其能力的绝对极限。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4AA0BB45D0A6782F.description3": "在大多数情况下，你会想要拥有高个体值的宝可梦。然而，个体值分布在哪些能力上同样重要。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4AA0BB45D0A6782F.description4": "例如，物理攻击手会希望拥有高&6HP&r、&6攻击&r、&6防御&r、&6特防&r和&6速度&r。特攻对于物理攻击手来说并不重要。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4AA0BB45D0A6782F.subtitle": "极限培育学！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4AA0BB45D0A6782F.task.8863340187297341083.title": "明白了！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4AA0BB45D0A6782F.title": "个体值详解",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4F8153DD174CECBF.description1": "世界各地散布着&6太阳团体战雕像&r，这些神秘的祭坛可以用&6Shift+右击&r激活以召唤注入了太阳能量的强大宝可梦。需要先击败它们才能捕捉。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4F8153DD174CECBF.description2": "生成的宝可梦的实力与稀有度将取决于雕像的&6阶级&r，以及首次激活时的生成池。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4F8153DD174CECBF.description3": "每个雕像每天可以挑战一次。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest4F8153DD174CECBF.task.515492914542016630.title": "找到一个&6太阳团体战雕像",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5172D7410B79BC65.description1": "With your guardian captured, it's not the end of your journey trainer journey.",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5172D7410B79BC65.description2": "&6Legendary Pokemon&r can be found in the world, through many different means.",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5172D7410B79BC65.description3": "Some will require you to solve puzzles or collect rare items. Others will test the limits of your farm.",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5172D7410B79BC65.description4": "Go out and catch them all!",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5172D7410B79BC65.description5": "&oSome more will be added in the next update of Society: Sunlit Cobblemon.&r",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5172D7410B79BC65.task.1956080571151526864.title": "Understood!",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5172D7410B79BC65.title": "The Hunt for Legendary Pokémon ",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest539CA5F135AA627D.description1": "每当你在&6训练家平台&r击败前来的挑战普通训练家并达成10连胜时，你将面对来自&6阳光联盟&r的训练家。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest539CA5F135AA627D.description2": "这些训练家会带着他们精心培育的伙伴来挑战你，非常有挑战性。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest539CA5F135AA627D.description3": "战胜这些训练家并获得&6阳光联盟勋章&r能证明你有资格领导道馆！你可以用勋章兑换一些稀有物品，或者纯粹用来炫耀。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest539CA5F135AA627D.subtitle": "接受考核！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest539CA5F135AA627D.title": "来自联盟的挑战",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5DCA4E4E712454CA.description1": "宝可梦的生成被划分为了不同的生成池：&6常见&r、&6罕见&r、&6稀有&r和&6极其稀有&r。每只宝可梦在各自的生成池中有着不同的生成几率！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5DCA4E4E712454CA.description2": "这可能会让寻找特定的宝可梦变得困难，&6宝可梦雷达&r能为你提供帮助！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5DCA4E4E712454CA.description3": "佩戴它后，可以在屏幕上显示附近区域内可生成的宝可梦，不过如果你将雷达设置为&6常见&r，你的屏幕大多数时候都会被塞得满满当当。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5DCA4E4E712454CA.title": "扫描宝可梦",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5E5313D628E28251.description1": "&6究极之洞发生器&r是一个奇特的装置，它能够同调阳光谷的宇宙频率。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5E5313D628E28251.description2": "为其注入&6宇宙尘埃&r来生成&b究极之洞&r，根据你当前所在的位置，它会从另一个维度带来&b究极异兽&r。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5E5313D628E28251.description3": "这个过程会激怒异兽，它们会汲取太阳的力量。需要先击败它们才能捕捉，建议使用究极球来捕捉它们。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest5E5313D628E28251.title": "究极之洞传送",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest60A705547AE0B95E.description1": "这么多农活，根本没时间外出训练你的队伍...",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest60A705547AE0B95E.description2": "不如试试让宝可梦来帮忙吧！它们可以协助农场里的各种工作，比如浇灌作物、砍树，以及快速熔炼矿石。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest60A705547AE0B95E.description3": "你的训练家等级越高，可以分配的工作就越多。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest60A705547AE0B95E.title": "让它们干活吧！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest612E6552C11E7D9B.description1": "击败持有太阳之力的强大宝可梦时，会掉落随机数量的&6太阳粒子&r！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest612E6552C11E7D9B.description2": "完成每天的挑战后，可以将这些太阳粒子重新供奉给&6太阳团战雕像&r以换取稀有物品。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest612E6552C11E7D9B.description3": "&o你的训练家阶级越高，太阳祭礼提供的奖励就越好...&r",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest612E6552C11E7D9B.title": "太阳粒子",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest621A320263EE43C2.description1": "如果你玩过方块宝可梦，可能会在想为什么到处都找不到疗草...",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest621A320263EE43C2.description2": "那是因为在几十年前，有一群大葱鸭入侵了山谷，把库存彻底消耗殆尽！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest621A320263EE43C2.description3": "在你掌握高级的农业技术之前，你需要从&6友好商店&r购买医疗用品。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest621A320263EE43C2.task.6366689056918305966.title": "明白了！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest621A320263EE43C2.title": "制作医疗用品？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest62276614C16063B7.description1": "影响宝可梦能力最重要的因素是它们的&6等级&r和&6种族值&r。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest62276614C16063B7.description2": "宝可梦的等级越高，就会变得越强。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest62276614C16063B7.description3": "种族值是由每种宝可梦的物种决定的。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest62276614C16063B7.description4": "&6个体值（IV）&r和&6基础点数（EV）&r决定了其余的能力数值。个体值对能力的提升幅度不算特别大，而基础点数可以通过正常游戏获得，因此大多数玩家不需要过于担心这些。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest62276614C16063B7.task.8304483815048173778.title": "明白了！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest62276614C16063B7.title": "宝可梦能力值",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest6366052B4FD5F516.description1": "击败某些宝可梦时会掉落&6神秘树枝&r！这种药草蕴含强大力量，可以供奉给&6太阳团战雕像&r以换取其他物品。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest6366052B4FD5F516.description2": "团战宝可梦的阶级越高，掉落的概率也越高。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest63B238596D407D9.description1": "&6阳山谷&r是未开发的全新地区！未被触及的土地上充满了野生宝可梦。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest63B238596D407D9.description2": "由于这里没有道馆，你需要用其他方式衡量自己的能力。阳光联盟将使用&6训练家等级&r系统来追踪你的成长！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest63B238596D407D9.description3": "随着你的农场发展和经验增长，你将从&6友好商店&r解锁更多交易、获得更多农场帮手，甚至有机会建立属于你自己的道馆...",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest63B238596D407D9.rich_description1": "前往训练家等级页面！（点击此处）",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest63B238596D407D9.title": "训练家等级",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest63B9101CAACBF5AE.description1": "&6树果奶昔&r是一种特殊配方，虫属性宝可梦可以将其加工成伤药！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest63B9101CAACBF5AE.description2": "由于&6药酿&r属于管制物品，这是你前期获取&6伤药&r或用来赚钱的主要途径之一...",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest63B9101CAACBF5AE.title": "特制奶昔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest68588C07B2EFCA55.description1": "欢迎来到&6阳光方可梦&r的世界；在这里，你可以一边经营农场，一边收集宝可梦！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest68588C07B2EFCA55.description2": "要开始你的旅途，你需要装备&6西尔佛检视镜&r。这个奇特的装置可以让你在世界中看到&6宝可梦&r！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest68588C07B2EFCA55.description3": "右键使用即可佩戴！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest68588C07B2EFCA55.task.7192841727701503607.title": "按&6M键选择初始宝可梦",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest68588C07B2EFCA55.task.8472653850254163461.title": "任意树果",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest68588C07B2EFCA55.title": "从方块宝可梦开始",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest68FCFC96B97D66A3.description1": "&6Worker Permits&r allow you to infinitely add worker slots! They aren't cheap, but they're the best way to maximize your farming potential as a master trainer.",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest68FCFC96B97D66A3.description2": "They can only be gotten once you reach the &6Prismatic Trainer tier&r. ",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75C2C4761B35739F.description1": "&6树果&r可以在世界各地的不同生物群系中找到。它们生长较慢，当种在耕地上后，每天早上都会额外生长一次。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75C2C4761B35739F.description2": "当宝可梦携带它们时，会在对战中产生不同的效果。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75C2C4761B35739F.task.3404886175882817940.title": "任意树果",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75C2C4761B35739F.title": "方可梦树果",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75DDF6E50DAD20F0.description1": "&6加工台&r可以让带有职能的宝可梦根据自身属性来制作不同物品。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75DDF6E50DAD20F0.description2": "-&6火属性&r：处理所有熔炉配方，并熏制鱼类",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75DDF6E50DAD20F0.description3": "-&6格斗属性&r：培育树苗并砍伐树木",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75DDF6E50DAD20F0.description4": "-&6毒属性&r：腌渍物品",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75DDF6E50DAD20F0.description5": "-&6电属性&r：为未充电的电池充电",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75DDF6E50DAD20F0.description6": "-&6超能力属性&r：制作宝可梦基因",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75DDF6E50DAD20F0.description7": "-&6钢属性&r：粉碎粗矿/垃圾回收",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75DDF6E50DAD20F0.description8": "-&6虫属性&r：将奶昔制成伤药",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest75DDF6E50DAD20F0.title": "让它们干活",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest771360679927C8E7.description1": "&6牧场小窝&r界面中的友好度由两项数值共同决定：",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest771360679927C8E7.description2": "-&6亲密度&r：根据当前数值与上限的差距，最多显示5颗心",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest771360679927C8E7.description3": "-&6生命值&r：根据当前数值接近270的程度，会显示5颗以上的爱心。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest771360679927C8E7.description4": "手动从宝可梦身上收获产物时，&6亲密度&r会提升，提升幅度取决于它最近食用的树果等级。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest771360679927C8E7.description5": "此外，通过对战、让其在精灵球外活动，以及使用某些消耗品也可以提升亲密度。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest771360679927C8E7.task.1104621425500371140.title": "友好度",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7B0A1FE4BD8D89B8.description1": "通过在战斗中击败特定宝可梦，可以获得对应的&6基础点数（EV）&r。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7B0A1FE4BD8D89B8.description2": "例如波波的速度种族值较高，击败一只波波后，你的宝可梦会获得1点速度基础点数。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7B0A1FE4BD8D89B8.description3": "每累积4点基础点数，总能力就会提升1点。基础点数总上限为&6510&r，且单项能力最多只能分配&6252&r点。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7B0A1FE4BD8D89B8.description4": "在进行基础点数训练时，通常会将&6252&r点分配给速度，再将&6252&r点分配给攻击（或特攻），剩余4点随意分配。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7B0A1FE4BD8D89B8.subtitle": "数值党专用！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7B0A1FE4BD8D89B8.task.9079675402624224047.title": "明白了！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7B0A1FE4BD8D89B8.title": "基础点数详解",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7B184B7096AC9BD8.description1": "&6绽放之环&r和&6贪婪号角&r是阳光谷中的秘密遗物，由农业与资本运作的极致所创造。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7B184B7096AC9BD8.description2": "将它们供奉给&6太阳团战雕像&r，分别可以召唤阳光形态的&6哲尔尼亚斯&r和&6伊裴尔塔尔&r。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7B184B7096AC9BD8.description3": "当你击败它们后，联盟会赠送&d大师球&r作为奖励，可以用来捕捉它们。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7B184B7096AC9BD8.subtitle": "&o推荐等级：60-80&r",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7B184B7096AC9BD8.title": "太阳守护者",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7D2F9E3B2518309C.description1": "装备&6西尔佛检视镜&r后，你发现了一只野生宝可梦！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7D2F9E3B2518309C.description2": "将准星对准它并按下&6R&r键即可发起战斗。你可以用初始宝可梦击败它，或者在其生命值较低时尝试捕捉。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7D2F9E3B2518309C.description3": "&o本任务线不仅仅讲解基础内容！即使你玩过方可梦/宝可梦，也建议阅读主线任务！&r",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7D2F9E3B2518309C.task.8525460108985779478.title": "发现一只宝可梦",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.quest7D2F9E3B2518309C.title": "发现宝可梦！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questB74FF8930C18079.description1": "When playing with friends, not being able to access each other's workstations can make things difficult.",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questB74FF8930C18079.description2": "The &6Public Contract&r will take one of your worker slots and infuse it in the machine, allowing anyone to put in or take out workers, without cost.",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questB74FF8930C18079.description3": "&cBe sure to claim areas your public workerstation is in, and only ally/team with those you trust! This makes your worker Pokemon able to be taken by others!&r",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questB74FF8930C18079.description4": "Break your own public workstation to get your worker slot back.",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questB74FF8930C18079.subtitle": "Use with care",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questB74FF8930C18079.title": "Sharing Workstations",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questCA36182D78C1214.description1": "&6阳光联盟&r会协助你发展农场！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questCA36182D78C1214.description2": "每当你击败一只野生宝可梦，联盟都会将资金直接打入你的账户。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questCA36182D78C1214.description3": "金额会根据你的训练家等级，以及所击败宝可梦的等级而变化。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questCA36182D78C1214.task.1930591335363882341.title": "达到嫩枝级",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questCA36182D78C1214.title": "农场资金",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questCA84740D7922353.description1": "友好商店是你购买精灵球、回复道具等训练家物资的一站式商店！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.ic__cobblemon.questCA84740D7922353.description2": "在较低的训练家等级时，商品种类会比较有限，但随着你能力的提升，联盟会为你提供更多货物。",
